E0045 (https://starstream.nightstream.dev/errors/E0045)

  x public binding `w` requires a public RHS; wrap private values with `disclose(...)`
   ,-[test.star:3:9]
 2 |     let pub mut w = x;
 3 |     w = y;
   :         ^
 4 | }
   `----
  help: `y` is a private parameter; declare it as `pub y: ...` in the function signature if callers should provide a public value here.
